.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
2 different games are played: backgammon, domino
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Birthday      | august        | may   |
| Game         | domino | backgammon |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

