2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person playing canasta is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | sprite      |
| Food          | asparagus | pomegranate |
| Game           | backgammon     | canasta      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
| Nationality           | british     | colombian      |
| Transport     | scooter   | bus         |

 